1. *Brata* su sada u školi. (The brothers are now in school.)
2. Oni su izgubili *brata*. (They lost their brother.)
3. Njegov *brat* je poznat u gradu. (His brother is famous in the town.)
4. Imamo dva *brata*. (We have two brothers.)
5. Moj *brat* je veoma uspešan. (My brother is very successful.)
6. Potrebna nam je još jedna stolica za *brata*. (We need another chair for the brother.)
7. *Bratu* se nikad ne žuri. (The brother never hurries.)
8. Ona je uvek tu da pomogne *bratu*. (She is always here to help her brother.)